"title": "5040: murder",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5040",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The unlawful killing of individual human beings, forbidden by God and carrying the threat of severe punishment.</p>\n<h2>Murder forbidden by the law</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:13\">EXO 20:13</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:17\">DEU 5:17</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:21\">MAT 5:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:18\">MAT 19:18</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:19\">MRK 10:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:20\">LUK 18:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:9\">ROM 13:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:9\">1TI 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:11-Jas2:12\">JAS 2:11–2:12</a></p>\n<h2>Murder is to be punished</h2>\n<h3>Punishment by death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:12\">EXO 21:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:6\">GEN 9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:17\">LEV 24:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev24:21\">LEV 24:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num35:16-Num35:21\">NUM 35:16–35:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num35:31\">NUM 35:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut19:11-Deut19:13\">DEU 19:11–19:13</a></p>\n<h3>Punishment by banishing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:13-Gen4:14\">GEN 4:13–4:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:17\">PRO 28:17</a></p>\n<h3>Punishment by exclusion from the kingdom</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:8\">REV 21:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:15\">REV 22:15</a></p>\n<h2>Unintentional murderers are protected from avengers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num35:11\">NUM 35:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num35:22-Num35:29\">NUM 35:22–35:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num35:32\">NUM 35:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh21:13\">JOS 21:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh21:21\">JOS 21:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh21:27\">JOS 21:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh21:32\">JOS 21:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh21:38\">JOS 21:38</a></p>\n<h2>Witnesses are required before murder is proven</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num35:30\">NUM 35:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:6\">DEU 17:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut19:15\">DEU 19:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:28\">HEB 10:28</a></p>\n<h2>Unpremeditated murder</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num35:22-Num35:24\">NUM 35:22–35:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:13\">EXO 21:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:41-Deut4:44\">DEU 4:41–4:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut19:4\">DEU 19:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh20:1-Josh20:3\">JOS 20:1–20:3</a></p>\n<h2>Premeditated motives of murder</h2>\n<h3>Jealousy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:8\">GEN 4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:12\">1JN 3:12</a></p>\n<h3>Lust</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:9-2Sam12:10\">2SA 12:9–12:10</a></strong> <em>Many motives contributed to David's plan to remove Uriah. It began with lust.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:1-2Sam11:17\">2SA 11:1–11:17</a></p>\n<h3>Rebellion and power</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs12:20\">2KI 12:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:21\">JDG 3:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:14\">2KI 9:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:24\">2KI 9:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:36-2Kgs19:37\">2KI 19:36–19:37</a></p>\n<h3>To remove opponents</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:25\">1KI 2:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg9:1-Judg9:6\">JDG 9:1–9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam20:9-2Sam20:10\">2SA 20:9–20:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:4\">2CH 21:4</a></p>\n<h3>To take revenge</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:28-2Sam13:29\">2SA 13:28–13:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:11-Exod2:13\">EXO 2:11–2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam3:27\">2SA 3:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam4:1-2Sam4:8\">2SA 4:1–4:8</a></p>\n<h3>Robbery</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:11-Prov1:13\">PRO 1:11–1:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:30\">LUK 10:30</a></p>\n<h3>Persecution</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:9\">MAT 24:9</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:12-Luke21:17\">LUK 21:12–21:17</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr21:13\">2CH 21:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job24:14\">JOB 24:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:10\">PRO 29:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:6-Matt14:11\">MAT 14:6–14:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:30-Matt23:37\">MAT 23:30–23:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:6\">MRK 3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:23\">ACT 2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:54-Acts7:60\">ACT 7:54–7:60</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:6\">2TI 4:6</a></p>\n<h2>Murder as an attitude as well as an action</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:21-Matt5:22\">MAT 5:21–5:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:19\">MAT 15:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:44\">JHN 8:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:15\">1JN 3:15</a></p>\n<h2>Murderers can be pardoned</h2>\n<h3>Unjustly</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:25\">LUK 23:25</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:15-Matt27:17\">MAT 27:15–27:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:6-Mark15:11\">MRK 15:6–15:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:39-John18:40\">JHN 18:39–18:40</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:14\">ACT 3:14</a></p>\n<h3>Justly--through God's grace</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:9-2Sam12:13\">2SA 12:9–12:13</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:10\">ACT 26:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:13-1Tim1:15\">1TI 1:13–1:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:12-Exod3:12\">EXO 2:12–3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:58\">ACT 7:58</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:3\">ACT 8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:1\">ACT 9:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:13\">ACT 9:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:4\">ACT 22:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:9\">1CO 15:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:8\">EPH 3:8</a></p>",
